item.title: About Me
item.description: Personal Life It’s interesting that you’ve found your way to this page, as there really isn’t a lot to say about me. I live a boring life in the small town of Denton, NE (current population 189), which is approximately 15 miles away from the center of the thriving medium-sized metropolis that is Lincoln, NE (born and raised).
